Author: tulipsandmothballs
Text: I can so relate. I planned IKEA on Friday. Budgeted calories for their meatballs and salmon. Drove 75 min. Walked around for N hour with my son before going to cafe. Cafe was CLOSED for a Swedish Orthodox Jewish Easter Passover thing. I was so mad and almost had a panic attack trying to find an alternative in a foreign part of town.
